# Theseus policy deltas against upstream defaults (90-systemd.preset).
# Must sort lexically BEFORE 90-systemd.preset: first matching rule wins.
# Units matched by no rule at all are enabled by preset-all's default.

# Display/login policy (getty vs greetd) lives in the greetd plan:
# 85-display-manager.preset.

# pcrlock.json hijacks systemd-cryptenroll enrollments; LUKS root uses
# PIN-only TPM2 binding (see README.md).
disable systemd-pcrlock-make-policy.service
